{"TopicId":156840,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Sandbox Contracts!","CreatedByName":"GhostboyDB","CreatedById":171695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-22T21:32:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"GhostboyDB","CreatedById":171695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-22T21:32:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you ever not known what to do in sandbox mode? have you \u00A0ever wanted to use GAP or DCA for contract configurator, But not wanted to pay for crafts, or do research? Me too. That\u0027s why I\u0027m asking for a tweak, because I don\u0027t know a thing about how to mod. I would appreciate a tweak to sandbox mode that adds the ability for you to get contracts.Say For DCA you want to do an attack on the island, or something but you want to use The nimitz from CVX or the Enterprise from aircraft carrier accessories. those things cost millions, and you don\u0027t want to spend that much on one contract, plus the cost of the aircraft. this is why i think it would be really helpful to allow you to open mission control in sandbox mode. although you would have to make the menu for contracts available too, it would be so much fun!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-22T21:32:47Z\u0022 title=\u002202/22/2017 09:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 22, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by GhostboyDB\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T08:06:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith a minute or two in setup work at the start, you can create yourself a \u0022career sandbox\u0022 without the need for any mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimply start in career mode, and use the Alt\u002BF12 menu to give yourself whatever funds and science points you need to max out all the buildings and unlock the entire tech tree. Add some reputation as well, so you get good contract assignments (or don\u0027t, if you want to work your way up yourself). Then keep adding more funds until your bank account is so well stocked that you aren\u0027t gonna run out anytime soon. And if you ever do run out, you can always add more.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd voila, there\u0027s your career sandbox! You can:\u003Cbr\u003E\n- build vessels without any constraints by parts or funds\u003Cbr\u003E\n- adopt strategies if you want, but you don\u0027t have to\u003Cbr\u003E\n- do contracts if you want, but you don\u0027t have to\u003Cbr\u003E\n- transmit science experiments if you want, but you don\u0027t have to\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only prerequisite to unlocking the full contract spectrum is that you need to get a vessel outside the atmosphere once. And remember: the further you fly, the further away the contract system will generate goals for you. If you want to do satellite contracts in Kerbin orbit, you should probably avoid going interplanetary for a while. Else you may be asked to do satellite contracts at Duna instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-23T08:07:24Z\u0022 title=\u002202/23/2017 08:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 23, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Streetwind\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-24T10:42:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/171695-ghostboydb/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022171695\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/171695-ghostboydb/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GhostboyDB\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/98962-streetwind/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002298962\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/98962-streetwind/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Streetwind\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/156510-12-career-manager-continued-for-all-your-career-mode-needs/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2956951\u0026amp;embedComment=2956951\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-2956951\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;line-height:22.4px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003EDescription:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;line-height:22.4px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nThis mod allows you to lock your funds and science at max, and also is bundled with complete reversibility. If that isn\u0027t enough, it also allows you to upgrade all buildings and topple the tech tree, again with full reversibility. It is a phenomenal mod for people who want to utilize some aspects of a career game (such as Kerbal Leveling) but without having to worry about money. I know you can partially do this with the debug menu, but I believe this can be much more elegant and again, has more features.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-24T10:50:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E really does have a mod for absolutely everything, doesn\u0027t he? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GhostboyDB","CreatedById":171695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-24T23:33:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222966233\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156840\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221487932940\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JadeOfMaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, JadeOfMaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca content